# This file exists only to make git track the results/ directory.
# After running train_qwen.py, this folder will contain:
#   qwen-astrologer-lora/    — LoRA adapter weights
#   qwen-astrologer-merged/  — adapter merged into base weights (for vLLM)
#
# Those subdirectories are excluded from git (.gitignore) because they
# contain large model files (.safetensors, .bin).
# Transfer them to your VPS via scp or push to Hugging Face Hub.
